### FUZZY QUERIES
### no tolerance
GET http://localhost:9200/movies/_search?pretty
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"query": {
		"match": {
			"title": "intersteller"
		}
	}
}

### set match to fuzzy and fuzziness of 1
GET http://localhost:9200/movies/_search?pretty
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"query": {
		"fuzzy": {
			"title": {
				"value": "intersteller",
				"fuzziness": 1
			}
		}
	}
}

