### prefix match the 2010s
GET http://localhost:9200/movies/_search?pretty
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"query": {
		"prefix": {
			"year": "201"
		}
	}
}

### wildcard query match the 1900s
GET http://localhost:9200/movies/_search?pretty
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"query": {
		"wildcard": {
			"year": "1*"
		}
	}
}